This folder will contain:

- High-fidelity UI mockups
- Mobile application screens
- Dashboard designs
- User flow diagrams
- Wireframes
- Design system documentation
- Brand assets
- Logo variations
- Icon library

---

# Vision

Every screen within the Survonomics ecosystem is designed with one objective:

**To make managing construction projects feel effortless, secure, and intuitive while maintaining the sophistication expected from enterprise software.**
